Package: margot.core
Title: Core S3 Classes and Infrastructure for the Margotsphere Ecosystem
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Bulbulia", , "joseph.bulbulia@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5861-2056"))
Description: Provides core S3 classes and infrastructure for the margotsphere 
    ecosystem. This package defines the fundamental data structures and 
    validation functions used across all margot packages, including the 
    margot_panel class for panel data, shadow classes for observational 
    distortions, and scenario classes for bundling shadows. Designed to be 
    lightweight with minimal dependencies.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/go-bayes/margot.core
